#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-07-05-recover-wsl-after-rancher.rst:8
msgid "Rancher利用後に壊れたWSL環境を再構築した手順"
msgstr "Steps to rebuild a broken WSL environment after using Rancher"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-07-05-recover-wsl-after-rancher.rst:10
msgid ""
"過去に Windows 上で Rancher を導入していた影響で、`wsl install` が正常に動作せず、WSL2 "
"を利用できない状態が続いていた。今回、その WSL 環境を完全に初期化し、再構築することに成功したので、その手順を記録しておく。"
msgstr ""
"Due to the fact that I had installed Rancher on Windows in the past, `wsl "
"install` did not work properly and I was unable to use WSL2. This time, I "
"was able to completely initialize and rebuild the WSL environment, so I will"
" record the steps."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-07-05-recover-wsl-after-rancher.rst:13
msgid "背景と問題の発生状況"
msgstr "Background and situation of the problem"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-07-05-recover-wsl-after-rancher.rst:15
msgid ""
"以前、Docker Desktop や Rancher Desktop を導入した経緯があり、WSL の仮想環境に `docker-desktop` や"
" `rancher-desktop` などのディストリビューションが自動で追加されていた。"
msgstr ""
"I had previously introduced Docker Desktop and Rancher Desktop, and "
"distributions such as `docker-desktop` and `rancher-desktop` were "
"automatically added to the WSL virtual environment."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-07-05-recover-wsl-after-rancher.rst:17
msgid ""
"これらをアンインストールした後も、`wsl install` コマンドがエラーを返すようになり、Ubuntu を含む WSL "
"環境の導入が一切できない状態に。"
msgstr ""
"Even after uninstalling these, the `wsl install` command returned an error, "
"making it impossible to install any WSL environment including Ubuntu."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-07-05-recover-wsl-after-rancher.rst:19
msgid "原因は、おそらく **WSLの内部状態が壊れていた** ことにある。"
msgstr "The cause is probably that the internal state of WSL was corrupted."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-07-05-recover-wsl-after-rancher.rst:22
msgid "解決のためのアプローチ"
msgstr "approach to solution"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-07-05-recover-wsl-after-rancher.rst:24
msgid "以下の手順で、WSL を一度完全に初期化し、再インストールを行った。"
msgstr ""
"I completely initialized WSL and reinstalled it using the following steps."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-07-05-recover-wsl-after-rancher.rst:26
msgid "**現在の WSL 状態の確認**"
msgstr "**Checking the current WSL status**"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-07-05-recover-wsl-after-rancher.rst:32
msgid "**不要なディストリビューションの削除**"
msgstr "**Remove unnecessary distributions**"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-07-05-recover-wsl-after-rancher.rst:40
msgid "**WSL 機能を完全に無効化**"
msgstr "**Completely disable WSL functionality**"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-07-05-recover-wsl-after-rancher.rst:47
msgid "再起動を実施。"
msgstr "Performed a reboot."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-07-05-recover-wsl-after-rancher.rst:49
msgid "**WSL 機能の再有効化**"
msgstr "**Re-enabling WSL functionality**"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-07-05-recover-wsl-after-rancher.rst:56
msgid "再び再起動。"
msgstr "Reboot again."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-07-05-recover-wsl-after-rancher.rst:58
msgid "**WSL の再インストール**"
msgstr "**Reinstall WSL**"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-07-05-recover-wsl-after-rancher.rst:64
msgid "これで再び Ubuntu などの WSL ディストリビューションがインストール可能な状態に戻った。"
msgstr "Now you can install WSL distributions such as Ubuntu again."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-07-05-recover-wsl-after-rancher.rst:67
msgid "今後の方針と教訓"
msgstr "Future policy and lessons learned"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-07-05-recover-wsl-after-rancher.rst:69
msgid "Rancher Desktop や Docker Desktop のアンインストール後でも、WSL 内部に痕跡が残っている場合がある。"
msgstr ""
"Even after uninstalling Rancher Desktop or Docker Desktop, traces may remain"
" inside WSL."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-07-05-recover-wsl-after-rancher.rst:70
msgid "**`wsl --unregister` + `dism` のセットによる初期化が有効** だった。"
msgstr "**Initialization by setting `wsl --unregister` + `dism` was valid**."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-07-05-recover-wsl-after-rancher.rst:71
msgid "開発マシンで仮想化関連ツールを切り替える場合は、WSL の状態管理にも注意が必要。"
msgstr ""
"When switching virtualization-related tools on a development machine, you "
"should also be careful about WSL state management."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-07-05-recover-wsl-after-rancher.rst:72
msgid "今後は WSL の破損時に備え、定期的な `wsl --export` によるバックアップも検討したい。"
msgstr ""
"In the future, I would like to consider periodically backing up using `wsl "
"--export` in case WSL becomes corrupted."

